# ============================================================
# Luxe Tracker — Vercel-only deployment
# ============================================================
# No environment variables required!
# All data lives in-memory (src/lib/data-snapshot.ts) and
# watchlist/alerts are persisted in localStorage.
#
# To scale beyond the seed baseline, edit BRAND_DEFS /
# PRODUCT_DEFS in src/lib/data-snapshot.ts and bump the
# expansion factor in the brand loop.
# ============================================================
